title: Famous birthdays for Oct. 26: Hillary Clinton, Keith Urban
text:
Oct. 26 (UPI) — Those born on this date are under the sign of Scorpio.

They include:

— Cereal foods entrepreneur C. W. Post in 1854

— Baseball Hall of Fame member Judy Johnson in 1900

— Boxing champion Primo Carnera in 1906

— Mohammad Reza Pahlavi, the last shah of Iran, in 1919

— Actor Bob Hoskins in 1942

— Author Pat Conroy in 1945

— Actor Jaclyn Smith in 1945 (age 74)

— TV personality Pat Sajak in 1946 (age 73)

— Former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton in 1947 (age 72)

— Rock musician Keith Strickland in 1953 (age 66)

— Actor James Pickens Jr. in 1954 (age 65)

— Actor Rita Wilson in 1956 (age 63)

— Bolivian President Evo Morales in 1959 (age 60)

— Actor Dylan McDermott in 1961 (age 58)

— Kenyan President Uhuru Kenyatta in 1961 (age 58)

— Actor Cary Elwes in 1962 (age 57)

— Actor Tom Cavanagh in 1963 (age 56)

— Singer Natalie Merchant in 1963 (age 56)

— Country singer Keith Urban in 1967 (age 52)

— Actor Seth MacFarlane in 1973 (age 46)

— Actor Jon Heder in 1977 (age 42)

— Wrestler CM Punk, born Phillip Jack Brooks, in 1978 (age 41)

— Actor Julian Dennison in 2002 (age 17)
